org.afplib.afplib

Interface IDEStructure

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IDEStructureImpl

    public interface IDEStructure
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'IDE Structure'.

    The following features are supported:

    • FLAGS
    • FORMAT
    • SIZE1
    • SIZE2
    • SIZE3
    • SIZE4

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getIDEStructure()
